<hr>

<p>WHAT MOTIVATES LEGALIZATION PROPONENTS? </p>

<hr>

<pre width="132">
<font size="2">           <b>DEA Statement</b>                         <b>The Facts</b>               

Some of the media, certain          The more interesting study of        
