    <p>City: <input type="text" size="25" maxlength="25"
    name="City">State: <input type="text" size="25"
    maxlength="25" name="State">Zip code: <input type="text"
    size="10" maxlength="10" name="Zip"> </p>
    <p>Telephone: <input type="text" size="25" maxlength="25"
    name="Phone"> </p>
    <p>If you are in a foreign country and your address doesn't
