<DOCHDR>
http://206.61.184.43:80/schaffer/Activist/junkemal.htm 206.61.184.43 19970122070702 text/html 3438
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 07:06:52 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N wpo-0deb)
Allow-ranges: bytes
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Saturday, 28-Dec-96 07:25:28 GMT
