<DOCHDR>
http://206.61.184.43:80/schaffer/DEBATE/MYTHS/myths4.htm 206.61.184.43 19970122034826 text/html 22944
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 03:48:17 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N wpo-0deb)
