Southeast Regional Center for Drug-Free Schools and Communities
Newsletter. See also Guy A. Cabral, &quot;Marijuana Decreases
Macrophage Antiviral and Antitumor Activities,&quot; Advances in
the Biosciences Vol. 80, 1991. </p>

