<p>Myths and Misconceptions of Drug Legalization: US Dept. of
Justice</p>

<h2>BIBLIOGRAPHY </h2>

<hr>

<p><img src="golddot1.gif" align="bottom" width="22" height="22"><b>Books</b>
</p>

