it Reserved for Drug Addicts,&quot; New York Times, February 11,
1992. </p>

<p>Collins, Christopher and Collins, Susan. &quot;What
Savings?&quot; The Sun, March 20, 1990. </p>

<p>Corcoran, David. &quot;Legalizing Drugs: Failures Spur
Debate,&quot; New York Times, November 27, </p>

<p>1989. </p>

