Smuggling,&quot; New York Times, May 8, 1993. </p>

<p>LaFranchi, Howard, &quot;Heavy Legal Drag Use in Spain Prompts
Calls for Tougher Laws,&quot; </p>

<p>Christian Science Monitor, November 7, 1991. </p>

